{"tid":936947,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[龜速更新] 以色列五日四夜之旅","createTime":"2018-12-11T07:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T06:44:23.000Z","uid":133680,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"122c6a96a48db932f37c5de97e8994997432e4e2","tid":936947,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:23:52.000Z","msg":"我最近清al,係搵唔到旅伴情況下，唯有自己一個人去以色列自由行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都多謝「路姆西遊世界」等巴絲advices,得以平安歸來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先貼左行程， 人左外地，有wifi會再更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1: Jerusalem, Nezareth (過夜only)<br />\nDay 2： Galilee &amp; Golan Heights<br />\nDay 3: Bethlehem, Herbon (Palestine)<br />\nDay 4：Masada, Ein Gedi, Deadsea, (Jericho), Jerusalem<br />\nDay 5: Tel-Alv, Yafo"},{"pid":"f0b2adec562afdc8aaedd2802a7ed8be63cba5d5","tid":936947,"uid":222136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:31:47.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9453386bb5e3b12eedc07b00a93518291f571e85","tid":936947,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:56:31.000Z","msg":"主要飛往以色列有三間航空公司：以色列航空， 俄羅斯航空及土耳其航空。 只有以色列航空為直飛航班， 俄航與土耳其航空價錢相近， 但漫長轉機等待時間（除非你想莫斯科半日遊）， 選擇自然只有土耳其航空。<br />\n<br />\n香港唱完美金後（以色列貨幣為新謝克爾，於香港比較難有兑換地方），飛機轉至伊斯坦堡機場， 往以色列飛機會有secruity check, 會要求搜身及搜袋， 於候機處只有我一個東亞人。<br />\n<br />\n到達以色列機場後， 關員會問你簡單數條問題：黎幾日，目的，住邊，呢度有冇識o既人，做邊行，公司名，無問題列印一張permit就會放行, 我直接坐機場巴士（37蚊， 機場只換左五十蚊美金）去Jerusalem"},{"pid":"7fa4ac951f0fb170ae5711e1f0227a6b967700dc","tid":936947,"uid":69695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T11:47:09.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49746dee1192507841a3414c11d1de88a5cd4702","tid":936947,"uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:15:17.000Z","msg":"Day 1: Jerusalem<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hUCgwGn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhUCgwGn.jpg&h=ab8a05b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n耶路撒冷落車後，我步行至舊城區大馬士革門（Damascus Gate), 據說現存城門為Ottoman時期所建。城門對出馬路為遍往西岸各城市巴士站，穿過大馬士革門就會係舊城阿拉伯區， 然後我會直接步行至西牆（ Western Wall), 又名哭牆。"},{"pid":"899a45a0e1b27ef47bbf2534884a48fc59acd59d","tid":936947,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:21:04.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c996f8907f12dde28623c6cf75663e8b74aeba6","tid":936947,"uid":183612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:23:04.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"850502bf86e449ad3181140cdb67fc3018fa9ec6","tid":936947,"uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:23:36.000Z","msg":"哭牆據說為古以色列時期所建， 古以色列亡國後， 猶太人都會到此哀痛國家亡國。1948年聯合國巴勒斯坦分治法案原定為第三方耶路撒冷特別市政權所控制， 卻於1948年以色列獨立戰爭為約旦吞併，猶太人足足十九年禁止進入西牆，直至1967年六日戰爭以色列攻入東耶路撒冷，西岸為止。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4hpR43P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4hpR43P.jpg&h=942ebec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FWyWwJ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWyWwJ1.jpg&h=66140eef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哭牆分為男女兩區"},{"pid":"460b691eacc580d0fc1c5ee49d0516c6a59795c3","tid":936947,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:24:29.000Z","msg":"5日就夠？"},{"pid":"1ed9cf294a3cf0c7f8ec8bae03adb15d47309910","tid":936947,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"460b691eacc580d0fc1c5ee49d0516c6a59795c3","tid":936947,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:24:29.000Z","msg":"5日就夠？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:25:40.000Z","msg":"又少少趕， 如果唔係之後約左人另一個trip, 我會改機票stay多幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9290cdbb19ef1d0fdb9b51ba9558a6a24dbd0e4","tid":936947,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"460b691eacc580d0fc1c5ee49d0516c6a59795c3","tid":936947,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:24:29.000Z","msg":"5日就夠？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:25:51.000Z","msg":"又少少趕， 如果唔係之後約左人另一個trip, 我會改機票stay多幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d58e8fd48b966dd4c273fa5ca3203844672feb6","tid":936947,"uid":176991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:26:31.000Z","msg":"由以色列去伯利恆，過關會唔會好耐好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2f9da0ee531a15095bcd8fefd2c46867fcde5a","tid":936947,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d58e8fd48b966dd4c273fa5ca3203844672feb6","tid":936947,"uid":176991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:26:31.000Z","msg":"由以色列去伯利恆，過關會唔會好耐好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:28:22.000Z","msg":"去無問題， 返黎會有check point , 軍人會拎埋支上埋實彈槍上車做安檢， 後面會再詳細講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8430f0739118264bbb274ef10bbdc8bb3f92413a","tid":936947,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"經過哭牆進入聖殿山， 以色列於內設有不少check point, 遊人需搜身搜袋通過安檢。以色列於其中一個檢查點特意貼上兩名殉職軍人相片，以醒目英文寫上佢地係死於恐怖襲擊，用意不得而知。 整過聖殿山最值得觀賞為金頂清真寺， 現只對伊斯蘭教徒開放。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKR5p8s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKR5p8s.jpg&h=853ea961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1aF9ROv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1aF9ROv.jpg&h=ea8e77fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c58a7e3054a0980c519666b01a5b0a1d79f9ddfc","tid":936947,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:47:51.000Z","msg":"之後我直接行路三十分鍾前往橄欖山，據聞為耶穌生前其中一傳道之地。日後羅馬圍攻耶路撒冷亦係安營此地。整個橄欖山滿佈教堂。其中最值得去就係山腳萬國教堂旁童女瑪利亞之墓， 入面有畫作講述神派天使賜予瑪利亞聖子，未有性行為懷孕，生子，再到耶穌受難一刻。內裡華麗宗教飾品，昏暗燈光，連我唔信神都對宗教肅然起敬。之後上山，會經過墓地山， 最後到達觀景台， 耶路撒冷舊城盡收眼底。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZKfYMxc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZKfYMxc.jpg&h=4001eb1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8kJC15z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8kJC15z.jpg&h=6ff24a1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f335a95a7e5cf070583cdeb05d953a183fd95bd","tid":936947,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"離開聖殿山就尋路前往Nazareth, 得一猶太教徒協助下順利中央巴士站，並前往海法，準備前往Nazareth. 但到達後發現巴士已開出，只有一架去Nazareth Lllit巴士， 幸得一猶太青年相助， 我得以係接近地點落車並同佢交換fb， 再行路過去， 因錯過hostel check in時間， 我直接walk in 一間酒店。及後問猶太青年西岸旅行之事， 佢只說作為以色列人非常不建議我前往，始終太危險。"},{"pid":"a9e9996af15df9965ccb2d2701e9fd6064a6898f","tid":936947,"uid":54990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T00:34:30.000Z","msg":"Jerusalem去機場火車通車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f784d2b1ffde8e31dc6e0a18dda476c89af1cb2","tid":936947,"uid":181852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T03:57:51.000Z","msg":"巴打你個行程chur到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係耶路撒冷我都留左5 日"},{"pid":"133233a9553d16dcd3020dbaacbcef908b845e86","tid":936947,"uid":54990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f784d2b1ffde8e31dc6e0a18dda476c89af1cb2","tid":936947,"uid":181852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T03:57:51.000Z","msg":"巴打你個行程chur到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係耶路撒冷我都留左5 日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:54:54.000Z","msg":"4-5日真係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9b4804d117824b47ea66dab50a1cbfc528a7c0","tid":936947,"uid":113929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1d58e8fd48b966dd4c273fa5ca3203844672feb6","tid":936947,"uid":176991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T12:26:31.000Z","msg":"由以色列去伯利恆，過關會唔會好耐好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:41:47.000Z","msg":"唔會，入巴勒斯坦境無人check , 入返以色列有關卡，巴勒斯坦自動落車比人 check , 但d軍人見你 東亞人樣都懶得check 你，仲撩你吹水"},{"pid":"c051bdafaa164cc6998e146d2ab8bcc6de85c469","tid":936947,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:05:35.000Z","msg":"lm爛尾"},{"pid":"22e352f03f01ac555a49a62b9e0423a42cb41e26","tid":936947,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T14:44:54.000Z","msg":"經過一日休息，第二日早餐未食情況就匆匆跳上day tour旅遊巴離開Nazareth。於公路遠眺城區時， 猶太司機稱城內猶太人同阿拉伯人和平共處。之後一行人直接Galilee自然保護區參觀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w78GRA1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw78GRA1.jpg&h=702f186e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n參觀完後一行人直接向戈蘭高地出發， 司機途中解釋戈蘭高地於六日戰爭為以色列由敘利亞奪取， 土地上敍利亞居民拒絕取得以色列國籍， 認為敍利亞終會取回戈蘭高地。 車上法國妹問以色列會歸回不屬於佢土地？ 司機只淡淡講一句：呢一刻仲係以色列土地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LbQh9pn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLbQh9pn.jpg&h=bcb004a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uoNAbCJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuoNAbCJ.jpg&h=5635f1f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（戈蘭高地， 接近敍利亞邊境）"},{"pid":"0627240c2adb6b1bffe1e22b2826e48bd7d18759","tid":936947,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T14:50:58.000Z","msg":"經過兩日舟車勞頓，加上hostel內訓得唔好， 第二朝十二點先起身， 打亂原定朝早去Ramallah， 晏畫去Bethlehem計劃。因而只有去Bethlehem, 並計劃之後直接返Jerusalem休息。"},{"pid":"2d60e7ef47cc11d0e00ec24bea79bfcea013cbc4","tid":936947,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T15:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68f2e57af5ecccf2d0538adbf7e3248a91083cc","tid":936947,"uid":88858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d60e7ef47cc11d0e00ec24bea79bfcea013cbc4","tid":936947,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T15:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T01:34:20.000Z","msg":"坐Royal Jordanian 最好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}